task.summary:
Project created in IntelliJ.
Added Card class and suit property.

Added rank property to Card class and getter method for rank.
Added Rank enum.
Added Deck class and deck collection. Also cardCount method. At present Deck's collection of cards is created empty.
Populated deck with cards. Created method to return deck.

Added Dealer class with deck property and shuffle method.
Refactored Deck class constructor to use fillDeck method to populate deck for each object.

Renamed deck in Dealer class to be dealerDeck for readability. Added dealCard method to Dealer.
Moved shuffle method to Deck class as it should be the responsibility of the Deck to carry out this action.
